The calculation of nucleon axial charges has been extended to those corresponding including strange quark currents. Then there are two more axial charges of the nucleon which recently

76

received special attention in the context of the "proton spin puzzle" [107]. The first one, g

8

A

is obtained by assuming a

\Gamma

